if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每個sem尾都咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果俾我返到a-level果里，我一定咁會咁做</blockquote><br />\nsem尾同自己講一日一課幾日就温哂<br />\n最後變左兩日温幾課"},{"pid":"6aac52ff6ebfdc96db2f8b42eca2e285a030a289","tid":30430,"uid":27105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:31:27.000Z","msg":"睇一次就識啦，書既野，温梨把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65263b7426b75902935c430dd88afebe9710a685","tid":30430,"uid":48491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:31:39.000Z","msg":"提升專注力嘅方法：<br />\n- 打少啲飛機<br />\n- 多飲水<br />\n- 放鬆心情<br />\n- 帶耳塞但係唔好聽歌<br />\n- 補充足夠糖分<br />\n- 充足睡眠<br />\n- 多啲唸下背唔好有咩後果自然唔敢分心<br />\n<br />\n有助短期轉長期記憶方法：<br />\n- 用關聯記憶法<br />\n- 用自己覺得比較有趣嘅方法背<br />\n- 瞓覺之前背<br />\n- 最好夜晚7至10點背，之後即刻瞓到天光"},{"pid":"d74939791c1caeeda65f47908248d07e9f8c44c5","tid":30430,"uid":21809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T16:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去自修室 因為我係果啲屋企溫唔到果啲人黎 <br />\n<br />\n跟住一路溫一路抄 會易入腦啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啊而且抄嘅時候試下將啲筆記轉做自己文字 一係趁禮拜五六夜媽媽半夜淨係開枱燈溫 個種氣氛好適合我溫 你可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738163fba8190ea994f6d4af2ee9521e7d60f89b","tid":30430,"uid":40993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T16:34:46.000Z","msg":"其實個個唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會一炮過溫兩三個鐘（極限 但deadline fighter會再多d）臨訓前係個腦到revise<br />\n會聽住歌溫 最好令你有動力既歌或者平靜既歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b9738ce3aa0a9307c238e3177dcdcbf31e5d34","tid":30430,"uid":40993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T16:35:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實個個唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會一炮過溫兩三個鐘（極限 但deadline fighter會再多d）臨訓前係個腦到revise<br />\n會聽住歌溫 最好令你有動力既歌或者平靜既歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講少左 會手抄自製雞精notes 幾有用 抄完會記得少少 同埋自己整雞精好方便萬一你唔記得即刻pick up返"},{"pid":"a2a496c5714c94072e9ed3ed935b6f6f4003cca1","tid":30430,"uid":19066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T16:44:24.000Z","msg":"搵個廢過你既人，教佢，教完自己就入哂腦"},{"pid":"36b2f84fc4b4c4be370cd779f5230b420ad66a38","tid":30430,"uid":43215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T04:52:57.000Z","msg":"final year 表示 睇住answer <br />\n溫書<br />\n成個sem 無上堂"}]}